<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Platform</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6;">
    <div style="max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <!-- Welcome Header -->
        <h1 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Welcome, <%= name %>!
        </h1>

        <!-- Welcome Message -->
        <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 16px;">
            Thank you for joining our platform. We are excited to have you with us. Explore, create, and manage your posts with ease.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <div style="margin: 32px 0;">
            <a href="http://localhost:3000/users/signin" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #4f46e5; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">
                Log in to your account
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 16px;">
            If you have any questions or need support, feel free to reach out. We're here to help.
        </p>

        <!-- Footer / Sign-off -->
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-top: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0;">Best regards,</p>
            <strong style="color: #334155;">The Platform Team</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>